title: ALIA - Budget. Save. Consult.

creator: Chat ALIA Dev Team
descriptionHtml:
Alia is a personal finance and budgeting tool that helps you track expenses automatically and save money. Our data shows Alia can save you up to Rp12,000,000 every year! Our finance app uses state of the art technology to analyse your accounts and give you the power to make smarter budgeting decisions with your money.

FEATURES

● See all your accounts in one place
● Track your spending & expenses
● Set budgets and track paydays
● Save money every month
● Access to consult with our financial manager
● Monthly and weekly report

BANK LEVEL SECURITY

● Alia uses SSL 256-bit encryption - the same security protocol that banks use - to ensure that your sensitive personal information is fully encrypted and securely stored.
● Alia does not store your online banking credentials.

OUR MISSION

We believe anyone deserves a financial advocate to help with money management and budgeting. Someone who watches our back no matter who we are and where we come from. We think we can provide a great experience, which relies on a basic principle, caring about our customers’ financial well being. This is who we are and what we stand for.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
ALIA just got smarter now, enjoy our new features!

What's New?

1. Tutorial mission (call to action)
2. New look bank integration feature

We also have improved several bugs from our last version.

We carefully read your reviews, so feel free to write about the features you like in the app and suggest the things you'd like to change. Feel free to drop us an email at admin@chatalia.id if you have any feedback.

creator: Sribuu Dev Team
descriptionHtml:
Sribuu is a personal financial management app that helps your to control your spending better.

We have helped #Sribuusquad to improve their financial health and save 30% more. Sribuu leverages Artificial Intelligence to analyze your spending habit and gives you best financial recommendations from budgeting to financial health, and how to reach financial your financial goals smarter.

Features
● Track spending and income automatically from bank and e-wallet
● Budget and automatic categorization
● Spending alert to avoid overspending
● Real-time money analysis and report
● AI Financial recommendations
● Saving tracker and financial goals
● Free consultation with Sribuu Financial Planner
● Bank-level security & privacy

Our mission
“Start from a thousand, for your million dreams”
We believe a thousand big things start from one smart step. With Sribuu, we want to invite you to start a new chapter in your life to reach financial wellness together!

Security
To keep our user data secured, Sribuu implements several steps:
● Encryption on transit. The connection between a user and Sribuu's server is encrypted using industry-standard (military-grade) SSL/TLS protocol. Use Sribuu app wherever and whenever without having to worry your connection is bugged.
● Server-side encryption. Sribuu always encrypts user's sensitive data stored in our server. Even if hackers or other attackers take control of our hardware, they cannot read Sribuu user data.
● Data ownership and privacy. We believe that only user owns their data, so Sribuu users can add, change, or delete their data whenever they want.

Join over thousands of members who trust Sribuu to save more, spend less, & track their transactions in our all-in-one personal finance app.
